<v Viking (Terry Gilliam)>
… was wearing…

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
<v Professor (Eric Idle)>
… in yesterday's raid on Selfridges.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.500
<v Assistant (Carol Cleveland)>
I'll carry out tests on it straight away, professor.

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:42.000
[action] She opens another lab door: it's full of cricketers.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.000
<v Cricketer (John Cleese)>
